Task Involved:
Extracting product data such as it's title, price and keeping tab on the price details by automating the data extraction process.

Process:
1- Imported required libraries such as beautifulsoup, requests, time and datetime.
2- Then wrote the code to establish connection with a website and extract the data.
3- Performed data cleaning and created a CSV file to store the extracted data.
4- Combined all of the code into a single function.
5- Added while loop and timer to automate the process.

Tools used: Python, Jupyter Notebook, BeatifulSoup library
